"\"<div><p data-start=\\\"176\\\" data-end=\\\"328\\\">This dual-workshop experience is designed to develop well-rounded, people-first leaders who can drive results while cultivating a thriving work culture.<\/p><p data-start=\\\"176\\\" data-end=\\\"328\\\"><br><\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"330\\\" data-end=\\\"606\\\">In <strong data-start=\\\"333\\\" data-end=\\\"363\\\">Sales Leadership in Action<\/strong>, participants will gain practical tools to lead high-performing sales teams by building trust, aligning goals, and driving accountability. The session focuses on real-world strategies that empower leaders to inspire and influence with impact.<\/p><p data-start=\\\"330\\\" data-end=\\\"606\\\"><br><\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"608\\\" data-end=\\\"904\\\">In <strong data-start=\\\"611\\\" data-end=\\\"643\\\">Happy Teams, Healthy Results<\/strong>, the focus shifts to the heart of organizational success\u2014employee well-being. Participants will explore how to recognize and reduce burnout, create psychologically safe environments, and implement wellness-centered practices that boost morale and productivity.<\/p><p data-start=\\\"608\\\" data-end=\\\"904\\\"><br><\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"906\\\" data-end=\\\"1113\\\">Together, these workshops provide a holistic leadership approach that connects performance with purpose, and results with relationships\u2014equipping today\u2019s leaders to succeed through both strategy and empathy.<\/p><\/div><div><br><\/div>\""